  m_text: "Level 8 \u2014 A spring launches the ball at a 45\xB0 angle. Its spring
    constant is 3000N and its displacement is \u22120.6m. The ball must clear a 20m
    gap to land on the castle, starting 1.5m above the launch point. What mass does
    the ball need to be to reach the castle? \nHINT: Every collision is perfectly
    elastic."
